title: Marksmanship and Sniping Literature Collection
description:
Here is a collection of books regarding marksmanship and sniping.  These guides are both for handguns and long guns.  Most of them are military manuals, but a few are books.  I also threw in "The .50 Caliber Rifle Construction," and "The Ultimate Sniper."  A nice collection of books to have for today&#039;s marksmen.
~~~
